RUN!
ID:NAMED RESTART
DESCRIPTION:Restarts named
PROVIDES:dns
BOUND:---
---
/etc/init.d/named restart
---



RUN!
ID:NTP RESTART
DESCRIPTION:Restarts ntpd
PROVIDES:ntp
BOUND:---
---
-/etc/init.d/ntpd stop
ntpdate 0.centos.pool.ntp.org
/etc/init.d/ntpd restart
---



